author: busted1
title: My life
body:
Life is always said to be life, life is sweet interesting and fantastic but that when you have the real and good people around you. When I was young I had a dream of becoming a great person in life and exhibits life at it fullest, live it the way I want and do things as I desire.

![images.jpeg](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmTuLgdqYq2dpQpUx4cbWAMA6rEP7RmeDnyY2qyQHzRJTi/images.jpeg)

To my very acts of thoughts, I've never put myself to a limitation and never ever underestimates my ability to be whom I said I wanna be. I face life as a war I need to conquer, putting on the spirits of a triumphant. 

 My life is my life. 
I live a life of creativity and a gifted one beyond my knowledge, i have never regretted i was born to life but to live a thankful one ahead and show more appreciation to God who created heaven and health.

author: busted1
title: Love Is A Beautiful Thing
body:
https://www.incimages.com/uploaded_files/image/1940x900/getty_871476054_362833.jpg
[source](https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&source=images&cd=&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=2ahUKEwiJ0emDiJHjAhUNdBQKHbZsCpQQjhx6BAgBEAM&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inc.com%2Fpeter-economy%2Flove-four-letter-word-or-remarkably-powerful-secret-for-business-success.html&psig=AOvVaw0F40SKkS9RfCKfWn8a2_w1&ust=1561979176998502)

Love is what rules the world. You cannot love yourself only, you need to love yourself as much as you love yourself. Love is a beautiful thing and love is great.
